raw_meta_yaml:
schema_version: 1

context:
  name: fpsim2
  version: 0.7.3

package:
  name: ${{ name|lower }}
  version: ${{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.org/packages/source/${{ name[0] }}/${{ name }}/fpsim2-${{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: d8da3fd37c707db459edeab72c9c70fe3986aeefd463352da0cbcef780341d53

build:
  number: 3
  skip: match(python, "<3.10")
  script: ${{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv --no-deps --no-build-isolation
  python:
    entry_points:
      - fpsim2-create-db = FPSim2.scripts.create_fpsim2_fp_db:main

requirements:
  build:
    - if: build_platform != target_platform
      then:
        - python
        - cross-python_${{ target_platform }}
        - numpy

    - ${{ compiler('c') }}
    - ${{ compiler('cxx') }}
    - ${{ stdlib("c") }}
  host:
    - python
    - pybind11 >=2.2
    - numpy
    - setuptools >=61.0.0
    - pip
  run:
    - python
    - rdkit >=2022.3.3
    - pytables >=3.10
    - sqlalchemy >=1.4.47
    - scipy
    - tqdm
    - numpy

tests:
  - python:
      imports:
        - FPSim2
      pip_check: true
  - script:
      - fpsim2-create-db --help

about:
  summary: Simple package for fast molecular similarity searching
  license: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE
  homepage: https://github.com/chembl/FPSim2

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - hadim
    - eloyfelix
